The liftgate has programmable heights, and Front and Rear Automatic Braking that works in conjunction with a short-radar and ultra-sonic sensors for safety reasons. For drivers, a Front Seat Center-Mounted air bag has also been tossed into the mix. There’s a Driver Awareness package with a variety of safety features, such as lane departure warnings, safety belt tightening when a crash is anticipated, and more.
